{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Remove speed limits on motorways",
        "additional_details": "Germany has unlimited sections so we think we should be in line with them. We think this would bring England out of the Stone Age.",
        "background": "We think it's about time the motorway speed limit was removed. Cars are safer than they used to be. We believe that driving at high speed is safer as you look at the road ahead far more.",
